The [[Bayer designation]] '''Epsilon Arae''' (ε Ara / ε Arae) is shared by two [[star system]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Ara (constellation)|Ara]]: * [[Epsilon¹ Arae|ε<sup>1</sup> Arae]] * [[Epsilon² Arae|ε<sup>2</sup> Arae]] They are separated by 0.54° on the sky.
