y 2005|publisher=Abhinav Publications|isbn=978-81-7017-415-8|ref=harv}} *{{cite book|last= Sharma |first=Usha |title=Festivals In Indian Society (2 Vols. Set)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Z6OYRUEAF7oC&pg=PA68|date=1 January 2008|publisher=Mittal Publications|isbn=978-81-8324-113-7|ref=harv}} *{{cite book|last= Verma |first=Manish |title=Fasts & Festivals Of India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=z4gzFFLdBoYC&pg=PA37|year=2000|publisher=Diamond Pocket Books (P) Ltd.|isbn=978-81-7182-076-4|ref=harv}}
